ORDER
PER CURIAM
AND NOW, this 28th day of September, 2016, the order of the Commonwealth Court is hereby AFFIRMED. Quest Diagnostics Venture, LLC’s Application for Relief Pursuant to Appellate Rule 123 to Grant Oral Argument is hereby DENIED as moot.
